    Prometheus -->|"HTTP/8080<br/>No encryption<br/>No auth"| MetricsSrv
    TrainingPod -.->|"K8s API<br/>PodGroup CRD"| Volcano
    TrainingPod -.->|"K8s API<br/>PodGroup CRD"| SchedPlugins

